 My dust cover had a big gob of silicone over the speedo end. I removed itand
removed the circlip and pulled the cable out the back a bit and tierapped it
in place. Now I don't have to listen to the aweful noise of itdestroying
itself. Just have to get a new one at some point will try aFLAPS when I get to
