-----------------------------------------------------

When my daughters rpm counter froze and took out the top end of the lower
cable; I found that neither the upper or lower cable is available anymore.
Only the one-piece earlier is available so the rpm counter is out of the
system. The one-piece cable is part number 211 957 801 F.
http://www.busdepot.com/details.jsp?partnumber=211957801F

